author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Cellcast denies Google in talks to use its technology
text:
Aug 17 Cellcast Plc :
* Statement re press speculation and price movement
* Notes recent press speculation suggesting that Google Inc in advanced talks with co to use their internet telephony technology
* Board confirms there is no truth in article and knows of no reason for price rise Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
